## FAILURE-SCENARIOS coverage

Every row in [FAILURE-SCENARIOS.md](../docs/FAILURE-SCENARIOS.md) needs tests by Phase 3 (integration) and Phase 5 (e2e where applicable):

| Scenario | Min test tier by Phase 3 |
|----------|--------------------------|
| Hold fails | integration |
| Order fails after hold | integration + component |
| Hold expires | integration |
| Duplicate confirm | integration |
| Timeout reconciliation | integration |
| Upstream unavailable | integration |

Do not merge flow changes without updating the matrix row and sequence doc.

