## Observability in tests

Integration tests should assert observability headers:

```python
assert response.headers["X-Request-ID"]
assert response.headers["X-Correlation-ID"]
assert "trace_id" in response.json()
```

Gateway contract tests (Phase 2) assert outbound headers on mocked transport.

Structured log fields to verify in critical path tests (when log capture added):

```json
{ "request_id", "correlation_id", "trace_id", "hold_id", "order_id", "step" }
```

See [docs/OBSERVABILITY.md](../docs/OBSERVABILITY.md).

