## PERFORMANCE policies

### Retry

| Operation | Policy |
|-----------|--------|
| GET (reconciliation) | Up to 2 retries with backoff |
| POST without idempotency | No blind retry |
| POST with idempotency + timeout | 1 retry, then reconcile |

### Timeouts (initial — tune in Phase 2)

| Upstream | Connect | Read |
|----------|---------|------|
| IHMS | 2s | 5s |
| EC-OPS | 2s | 10s |

Document changes in PERFORMANCE.md when values change.

### Connection pooling

- One `httpx.AsyncClient` per upstream in app lifespan
- Never create new client per request

### Async

- Use `async def` for I/O bound route handlers and gateway methods
- No blocking calls in request path

